          }
        },
        "expectedDifferences": [
          {
            "path": "$.unpinnedDefinition.id",
            "matcher": "shopify-gid:MetafieldDefinition",
            "reason": "The proxy unpins the locally staged synthetic definition ID while Shopify returned the live-store definition ID."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  "notes": "HAR-699 captures the default 2025-01 Shopify product-owner cap of 20 pinned metafield definitions. The live capture temporarily unpins existing product definitions so the scenario can create and pin exactly 20 disposable definitions, observes `PINNED_LIMIT_REACHED` on the 21st pin, verifies constrained definitions return `UNSUPPORTED_PINNING`, lists the 20 pinned definitions in descending `PINNED_POSITION` order, and then unpins one definition to keep compaction covered."
